  ('medical-tech-moex-12881', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-101-716b3930', 'sub-medical-tech-07', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關臨床上常見的腸球菌菌種（Enterococcus spp.）之特性，下列敘述何項錯誤？', '["可在10℃或45℃生長", "PYR（pyrrolidonyl arylamidase）及LAP（leucine aminopeptidase）試驗陽性", "E. faecium對penicillin的抗藥性比E. faecalis強", "大部分菌株在綿羊血BAP上形成小點狀β-溶血型菌落"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1b2dc04cf866", "answer_pdf_sha1": "24541fc8fb91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "108", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
